{
  "stem": "833.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was just some-- somebody lost it on the-- and I thought, this is a good-- a good tool, a tool for freedom, because I'm-- the Prussian spirit is a spirit that has to be lived.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It cannot be explained.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anything that is-- looks like official-- anything that looks like something that has been ordered to do-- that has nothing to do with work of prisoner is correct.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's that-- that Prussian spirit.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You cannot explain it exactly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I-- but I've learned it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I took that next morning from the work-- went away and started measuring every distance whenever I saw an officer coming up.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they passed by, didn't pay any attention to me, because I was measuring something with an official tool.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So now we'll-- we'll go ahead-- as much as I would love to hear the details, I know you're tiring.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now talk about-- your father was in England, and he was able to arrange for--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, he was in England, but he went to Paris.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see, the thing was that the rules were-- it took quite some time until-- until the-- the rules of-- of-- of exodus of Jews was allowed.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was, I think, by December or January that these rules were promulgated, announced.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The German-- the German who--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] what name did you say?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, not Schindler.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The man who was hanged.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Eichmann, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Eichmann was in charge in Vienna about the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he got the rules from Germany, and it was then known that one could get out of a concentration camp if-- if I was able to immigrate into a foreign country-- foreign country outside of Europe and outside of the United States.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That means it could have been South America.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
